{"tid":368424,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人好掛住以前台灣明星紅嗰時 咁就10年","createTime":"2017-08-21T14:06:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-22T07:49:05.000Z","uid":75297,"like":17,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"dafb1ad242b338ca99492bfcb582b8bc05d70e58","tid":368424,"uid":75297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T14:06:08.000Z","msg":"仲記得嗰時台灣D明星紅到個個同學都煲台劇<br />\n不停loop佢地既歌<br />\n<br />\n自己仲會走幾檔報攤買Yes!! 為嘅就係Yes!!夾住印住偶像樣嘅風扇/海報/書籤<br />\n仲會儲住D封面貼喺房門口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然依家諗返都覺得嗰時好on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但真心當年既台劇好好睇 D歌又好聽<br />\n<br />\n而且當年學生妹都清純D <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 依家周街化曬韓妝 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又聽埋d唔知唱乜嘅歌 肯定又有人話d韓星好努力乜乜乜 但個feel真係唔同曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n頭先上網見到183Club仲重現螢幕 真係百感交集<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nLink: <a href=\"https://youtu.be/99DT_tDU614?t=34s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F99DT_tDU614%3Ft%3D34s&d=T5GqAMoknpQKFzmuFUSIu5ZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=c422b045\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/99DT_tDU614?t=34s</a><br />\n有冇人都好掛住以前台灣明星紅嗰時？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef6ff929fc35641f8bffe87686aa3201e9efe9dd","tid":368424,"uid":75297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T14:13:14.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"2f64db8bc3299d829997a940ed6d4f5b35a9dfbe","tid":368424,"uid":75297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T14:17:56.000Z","msg":"嗰種感覺唔會再返到嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3febf16d32dad7ed9ed55c4249b7d22ea86211b9","tid":368424,"uid":62502,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T14:22:10.000Z","msg":"好過睇韓劇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9e5a72c054eace86117f9bd5b1319da9b45119f","tid":368424,"uid":68887,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T14:32:23.000Z","msg":"Agger<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n認真討論<br />\n當年台灣嘅偶像咪又係被大把人踩話mk<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n就歌方面<br />\n可能係因為相同嘅文字同相近嘅文代<br />\n而台灣國語又係我地由細學到大<br />\n會容易d理解歌詞背後嘅意思"},{"pid":"6df884a20d3fcae1f881e38c67bfcabc4c7a4e17","tid":368424,"uid":68887,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T14:34:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Agger<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n認真討論<br />\n當年台灣嘅偶像咪又係被大把人踩話mk<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n就歌方面<br />\n可能係因為相同嘅文字同相近嘅文<span style=\"color: red;\">化</span><br />\n而台灣國語又係我地由細學到大<br />\n會容易d理解歌詞背後嘅意思</blockquote><br />\n錯字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"798e0bd3b7b88491772d018dbb6ab93b31523284","tid":368424,"uid":62502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T14:47:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Agger<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n認真討論<br />\n當年台灣嘅偶像咪又係被大把人踩話mk<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n就歌方面<br />\n可能係因為相同嘅文字同相近嘅文<span style=\"color: red;\">化</span><br />\n而台灣國語又係我地由細學到大<br />\n會容易d理解歌詞背後嘅意思</blockquote><br />\n錯字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n可能因為太易理解所以台風咁快完，少左慢慢理解發掘個一步，聽得深度唔夠，浪費左好多好歌同歌手"},{"pid":"1a717673ebe2b44bee8a357a2af53b9e2ace6ecd","tid":368424,"uid":116530,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T14:49:34.000Z","msg":"飛輪海<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 棒棒堂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01d9703c54a1348bb16a32ff6056ded78d4e0941","tid":368424,"uid":65979,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T14:55:59.000Z","msg":"嗰陣J2 會播天才衝衝衝<br />\n艾莉絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"449c08d8a0a22c163acccfdb1c84963d8e988c0b","tid":368424,"uid":75297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T15:04:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>嗰陣J2 會播天才衝衝衝<br />\n艾莉絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n嗰陣D台灣綜藝真係好好笑<br />\n仲有康熙來了 你猜你猜你猜猜猜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a5c9993f81253c53b943ef5ecdd5ff104e4fcf4","tid":368424,"uid":68887,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T15:09:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Agger<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n認真討論<br />\n當年台灣嘅偶像咪又係被大把人踩話mk<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n就歌方面<br />\n可能係因為相同嘅文字同相近嘅文<span style=\"color: red;\">化</span><br />\n而台灣國語又係我地由細學到大<br />\n會容易d理解歌詞背後嘅意思</blockquote><br />\n錯字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n可能因為太易理解所以台風咁快完，少左慢慢理解發掘個一步，聽得深度唔夠，浪費左好多好歌同歌手</blockquote><br />\n在下認為唔太關事<br />\n台灣娛樂產業輸出差左<br />\n其一主要係投入嘅資源唔多 始終台灣人嘅收入人人22k<br />\n即使係當紅藝人其實都唔係搵多好多<br />\n而同時間中國又係咁借機以錢去買人材<br />\n好多香港同台灣演藝人/幕後都過左去搵錢<br />\n其二係紅得太快<br />\n多左好多台灣本地人有樣學樣咁推出一大推人<br />\n原有嘅公司又食住個勢又係咁推一大堆人<br />\n搞到資素差左<br />\n好似棒棒堂二軍都未正式出道個節目就進階又搞正三軍<br />\n終極系列無啦啦又係咁出 就係為左捧隊武虎將同speXial等等<br />\n其三  槍打出頭鳥<br />\n有人迷就有人踩 唔鐘意依種文化嘅人係咁攻擊<br />\n咁踩踩法最後咪連灰都冇囉"},{"pid":"4cdaec0b49e088420bec033c5a4d0e10a902d244","tid":368424,"uid":106584,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T15:12:31.000Z","msg":"棒棒堂，黑澀會，康熙來了&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n惡作劇之吻，惡魔在身邊，王子變青蛙，轉角通到愛，MVP情人&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n咁就十年喇原來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c496e485252f91ad7eb008c0a7d5a950bedf0b51","tid":368424,"uid":106584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T15:13:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>棒棒堂，黑澀會，康熙來了&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n惡作劇之吻，惡魔在身邊，王子變青蛙，轉角<span style=\"color: red;\">通</span>到愛，MVP情人&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n咁就十年喇原來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">遇</span>"},{"pid":"582ade367f8c47ea05130d27a3af28124dc68629","tid":368424,"uid":75297,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T15:15:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Agger<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n認真討論<br />\n當年台灣嘅偶像咪又係被大把人踩話mk<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n就歌方面<br />\n可能係因為相同嘅文字同相近嘅文<span style=\"color: red;\">化</span><br />\n而台灣國語又係我地由細學到大<br />\n會容易d理解歌詞背後嘅意思</blockquote><br />\n錯字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n可能因為太易理解所以台風咁快完，少左慢慢理解發掘個一步，聽得深度唔夠，浪費左好多好歌同歌手</blockquote><br />\n當年D組合都陸陸續續解散<br />\n傳聞當年某4人極紅組合好似因爲某個團員係hehe<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲嚇到另一個團員<br />\n最終都係解散埋 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 然後人氣都每況愈下<br />\n有次見到某成員都成3x歲仲要出嚟拍返青春偶像劇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6919f6b0014566ad67335d8bb7bf5c24951b13d","tid":368424,"uid":62289,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T15:17:10.000Z","msg":"花無百日紅 <br />\